---
title: Salsa Verde Enchiladas with Southwest Crema & Refried Beans
description: Saucy, smothered, hearty, and delicious: This vegetarian enchilada bake has it all, plus it’s perfect for a crowd! You’ll wrap tortillas around Tex-Mex-spiced bell pepper, tomato, and refried beans, top with mild green salsa and our melty Mexican cheese blend, pop it in the oven till it’s piping hot and bubbly, then straight to the table family style with a final drizzle of spiced crema.

*This recipe is double the typical servings, providing 4 servings and 8 servings for a 2 person and 4 person box respectively.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6716a67fffa4e28ccb95eb4f-a0ee06ea.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/6716a67fffa4e28ccb95eb4f-en-US.pdf
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/salsa-verde-enchiladas-6716a67fffa4e28ccb95eb4f
cuisine: Mexican
time required: 35 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 650 kcal
  fat: 22 g
  saturated fat: 9 g
  carbohydrates: 86 g
  sugar: 13 g
